  { name: "Confidential Marketing", body: "Your business is marketed discreetly to a vetted buyer pool, so employees, customers, and competitors do not find out." },
  { name: "Buyer Screening", body: "Every prospective buyer is qualified for financial capacity and fit before they ever see your numbers or your name." },
  { name: "Offers and Negotiation", body: "Phil negotiates price and terms on your behalf, with the experience of more than two decades of Arizona deals behind every move." },
  { name: "Due Diligence", body: "We manage the document requests, the lender, and the timeline so the deal keeps moving and nothing stalls." },
