<Layout
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  canonical="/peoria-business-broker-test/"
  ogImage={ogImage}
  ogImageAlt="Peoria Business Broker Phil Reese"
  ogImageWidth={1200}
  ogImageHeight={630}
  structuredData={structuredData}
  noIndex={true}
>
  <!-- 1. PEORIA HERO (bespoke) -->
  <section class="section pt-hero">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="pt-hero-inner">
        <p class="pt-eyebrow">Peoria, Arizona Certified Business Intermediary</p>
        <h1 class="pt-h1">Peoria Business Broker</h1>
        <p class="pt-sub">Sell your Peoria business quietly, or buy your next one, with Phil Reese, a Certified Business Intermediary who has helped Arizona owners since 2001. Start with a free, confidential valuation and know exactly where you stand.</p>
        <div class="pt-trust">
          <span>CBI and Master CBI</span>
          <span>Five-Star Rated on Google</span>
          <span>IBBA Chairman's Circle</span>
          <span>West USA Realty</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-cta-row">
          <a class="pt-btn pt-btn--primary" href="tel:+14807077721">Call Phil Direct: 480-707-7721</a>
          <a class="pt-btn pt-btn--ghost" href="#pt-contact">Get My Confidential Valuation</a>
        </div>
        <p class="pt-microcopy">Confidential from the first call. No obligation. Your employees, customers, and competitors are never contacted.</p>
        <p class="pt-buy-link"><a href="#pt-buy">Looking to buy a business in Peoria instead?</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. PEORIA INTRO (bespoke) -->
  <section class="section philo-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="txt-col">
        <p>To buy or sell a business in Peoria, you need a broker who actually knows the neighborhoods and the local economy. From the restaurants and bars along the <strong>P83 Entertainment District</strong> to the medical and dental practices off <strong>Bell Road</strong>, the franchises at <strong>Park West</strong>, and the fast-growing service companies out toward <strong>Lake Pleasant Parkway and Vistancia</strong>, Peoria runs on owner-operated businesses. <a href="/about/">Phil Reese</a> has spent more than two decades helping Arizona owners sell those companies for strong terms while protecting their confidentiality.</p>
        <p>Whether you are planning your exit, preparing for retirement, or ready to buy your first business, Phil gives you the clarity and the discretion the moment calls for. This is what a Peoria business sale should feel like: handled, quiet, and worth it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="img-col">
        <img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" src="/images/peoria-business-broker-test/hero.jpg" alt="A Peoria, Arizona commercial district where local businesses are bought and sold" width="480" height="360" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. phil-sctn — Meet Phil (VERBATIM from homepage) -->
  <section class="section phil-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="img-col">
        <img
          fetchpriority="high"
          src="/images/home/phil-reese-portrait.png"
          alt=""
          width="417"
          height="588"
          class="alignnone size-full"
          srcset="/images/home/phil-reese-portrait.png 417w, /images/home/phil-reese-portrait-213x300.png 213w"
          sizes="(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="txt-col">
        <h3 class="maintitle h3-style">Phil Reese</h3>
        <p>Selling a business is personal. I know because I’ve been in your shoes. In 1995, I co-founded First Impression Security Doors out of my garage in Mesa, growing it to a full manufacturing facility in Gilbert with 13 employees before a successful exit in 2001. That company has since grown into Arizona’s largest ornamental iron firm.</p>
        <p>Today, I use my over 20 years of Business Brokering expertise to help owners navigate their own exits. I am one of only four business brokers in the state to hold the Master Certified Business Intermediary (MCBI) designation. As the former Ethics Chairman for the Arizona Business Brokers Association (AZBBA), I prioritize confidentiality and integrity throughout the whole sales process, ensuring your legacy is protected.</p>
        <div class="btns btns-alt">
          <a href="/about/">Learn More About Phil</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. sold-sctn — Businesses sold (VERBATIM from homepage) -->
