        <span class="stpone">Step One</span>
        <img src="/images/home/selling-process-infographic.svg" alt="" width="834" height="875" class="alignnone size-full" loading="lazy" role="img" />
      </a>
      <ul class="mob-steps">
        <li class="stp-box"><p>Step One <br />Contact Phil</p></li>
        <li class="stp-box"><p>He’ll Determine the Value of Your Business</p></li>
        <li class="spt2" set:html={sptDividerSvg} />
        <li class="stp-box"><p>List Your Business</p></li>
        <li class="stp-box"><p>Go To Market</p></li>
        <li class="spt2" set:html={sptDividerSvg} />
        <li class="stp-box"><p>Screen Business Buyer Candidates</p></li>
        <li class="stp-box"><p>Buyer &amp; Seller Meeting</p></li>
        <li class="spt2" set:html={sptDividerSvg} />
        <li class="stp-box"><p>Buyer Makes An Offer</p></li>
        <li class="stp-box"><p>Buyer Does Due Diligence</p></li>
        <li class="spt2" set:html={sptDividerSvg} />
        <li class="stp-box"><p>Close on The Sale</p></li>
        <li class="stp-box"><p>Buyer Starts the Training Process</p></li>
        <li class="stp-box btns btns-alt"><a href="#pt-contact">Contact Phil</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 9. CONFIDENTIALITY (bespoke) -->
  <section class="section pt-quiet">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="pt-quiet-text">
        <h2 class="pt-h2">Your Sale Stays Quiet</h2>
        <p class="pt-lede">For most owners the biggest worry is not the price. It is that employees, customers, landlords, or competitors find out before the time is right. Here is how Phil keeps your sale confidential.</p>
        <ul class="pt-quiet-list">
          <li>Your business is never publicly listed with its name attached.</li>
          <li>Every buyer signs a confidentiality agreement before seeing your financials.</li>
          <li>Buyers are screened for funding and fit before they ever learn who you are.</li>
          <li>You control the timing, the message, and who finds out and when.</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="pt-btn pt-btn--primary" href="#pt-contact">Start A Private Conversation</a>
      </div>
      <div class="pt-quiet-img">
        <img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="/images/peoria-business-broker-test/process.jpg" alt="A confidential handshake closing a Peoria business sale" width="520" height="390" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 10. why-sctn — Five reasons (VERBATIM from homepage) -->
  <section class="section why-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="col-title">
        <h3 class="maintitle h3-style">Five of Many Reasons Why You Should Choose Phil Reese to Sell Your Business!</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="icon-box">
        <div class="icons-why" set:html={whyIcon1Svg} />
        <div>
          <h4 class="subtitle h5-style">Former <br />Business Owner</h4>
          <p>There’s a difference between studying business and running one, Phil has done both. He has owned and operated several businesses throughout his career. This first-hand experience allows him to represent sellers with true empathy and insight.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="icon-box">
        <div class="icons-why" set:html={whyIcon2Svg} />
        <div>
          <h4 class="subtitle h5-style">Master Certified Business Intermediary</h4>
          <p>Phil is one of only four business brokers in Arizona to hold the prestigious MCBI designation from the International Business Brokers Association (IBBA). This elite credential represents the gold standard in business brokerage, ensuring your sale is handled with the highest level of expertise.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="icon-box">
        <div class="icons-why">
          <img width="83" height="78" src="/images/home/badge-20-years.png" alt="20 years" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="subtitle h5-style">Over 20 Years Experience, Proven Award Winning Agent </h4>
          <p>Since 2001, Phil has closed over $97M in business sales across 100+ transaction. As a top 1% producer at West USA Realty and a multi-year IBBA Chairman’s Circle award winner, he combines decades of business brokering knowledge with a consistent, proven track record of results.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="icon-box">
        <div class="icons-why" set:html={whyIcon4Svg} />
        <div>
          <h4 class="subtitle h5-style">Free No-Obligation Valuations</h4>
          <p>Understanding your business’s true market value is the first step to a successful exit. Phil provides confidential, real-world valuations at no cost. Get an honest assessment of what your business could sell for based on current buyer demand and industry-specific data.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="icon-box">
        <div class="icons-why" set:html={whyIcon5Svg} />
        <div>
          <h4 class="subtitle h5-style">BBB Accredited, A+ Rated</h4>
          <p>Anyone can claim integrity—very few can prove it. BBB accreditation and an A+ rating reflect a verified track record of trust, ethical business practices, and accountability. Paired with Phil’s experience as former AZBBA Ethics Chairman, it ensures your transaction is handled with integrity, discretion, and unwavering professionalism.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 11. VALUATION CTA (bespoke) -->
  <section class="section pt-valuation">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="pt-val-card">
        <div class="pt-val-text">
